Package: forrest
Title: Publication-Ready Forest Plots
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Lorenzo", "Fabbri", email = "lorenzo.fabbri92sm@gmail.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
  )
Description: Creates publication-ready forest plots with minimal
    dependencies. Supports subgroup headers, summary estimates
    displayed as diamonds, grouped estimates with automatic color
    mapping, and customizable text columns alongside the plot.
    Works with base R data frames, 'tibble', and 'data.table'
    objects. Built on 'tinyplot' for clean, consistent visual styling.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
