    R (>= 4.1.0)
Imports:
    tinyplot (>= 0.2.0)
Suggests:
    data.table,
    knitr,
    rmarkdown,
    tibble,
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
Config/testthat/edition: 3
VignetteBuilder: knitr
